3-TASK
Role: Senior frontend engineer

Task:
Implement balance top-up feature, order payment logic, and fix dark mode issues

Tech Stack:
- Next.js 14 (App Router)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- shadcn/ui
- React Query
- Axios
- Zustand

--------------------------------
1. BALANCE TOP-UP FEATURE
--------------------------------

UI:
- Add "Top Up Balance" button in cabinet page
- On click → open modal

Modal:
- Input field (amount)
- Min: 10,000
- Max: 10,000,000
- Validation (number only)

Behavior:
- On submit:
  - Call API (e.g. POST /api/users/balance/top-up)
  - Send amount
  - Update user balance (refetch or state update)
  - Show success toast
  - Close modal

UX:
- Disable button if invalid input
- Show loading state

--------------------------------
2. ORDER PAYMENT LOGIC
--------------------------------

Context:
User places order from Cart page

Behavior:
- When clicking "Buy / Order":
  - Check user balance
  - If balance >= total price:
      → Call order API
      → Deduct balance
      → Show success message
  - If balance < total price:
      → Show error: "Insufficient balance"

Integration:
- Use React Query mutation
- Update UI after order success

--------------------------------
3. DARK MODE FIX
--------------------------------

Problem:
Dark mode is not working correctly inside components

Fix:
- Ensure Tailwind dark mode is enabled (class strategy)
- Add "dark" class on root (html/body)
- Use dark: variants in ALL components

Example:
- bg-white → dark:bg-gray-900
- text-black → dark:text-white
- border → dark:border-gray-700

Also:
- Fix shadcn/ui components to support dark mode
- Ensure consistency across pages

--------------------------------
OUTPUT
--------------------------------

- BalanceModal component
- Balance API integration
- Order logic implementation
- Cart page update
- Dark mode fixed components
- Clean production-ready code

--------------------------------
IMPORTANT
--------------------------------

- Think like senior engineer
- Keep logic clean and reusable
- Avoid duplicated code
- Ensure good UX
Also:
- Format currency (UZS)
- Add confirmation dialog before payment
- Animate modal (Framer Motion)